title: Opie & Jim Norton NOV 04 2015 Wed.mp3
description:
Opie & Jim Norton NOV 04 2015 Wed (03:00:39)


On Today's Show:

SHERROD SMALL, WHEELER WALKER Jr.

Sherrod Small is with Opie and Jimmy. They talk about a small plane that crash landed with a parachute, the Presidential candidates and political topics.

They talk about the parade for the Kansas City baseball team, Quentin Tarantino, and stupid political correctness stuff.

They talk about a guy who was out of town for surgery and returned to find his house was completely gone, a dog-fucking story, cops posing as homeless people to catch people texting while driving, and self-driving cars.

Country music guy Wheeler Walker, Jr. joins them on the phone from Nashville. They talk about his new song, "Fuck You, Bitch", and play it
